cloudy; Knoxville 65 foggy; Macon 71 partly cloudy; Miami 82 fair;
New York 63 cloudy; Philadelphia 63 rain; Pittsburgh 60 cloudy;
Portland, Me., 52 fair; Richmond 67 foggy; Tampa 82 fair;
Washington, D.C. 65 rain.
   _Central: Bismarck 40 windy; Chicago 64 hazy; Denver 50 fair;
Des Moines 61 windy; Indianapolis 65 foggy; Kansas City 66 fair;
Little Rock 66 fair; Nashville 63 fair; New Orleans 67 fair; North
Platte 47 fair; Oklahoma City 70 fair; Omaha 61 windy; Rapid City
41 windy; St. Louis 65 foggy; Minneapolis-St. Paul 51 thunderstorm;
Sault Ste. Marie 52 foggy; San Antonio 82 fair.
   _West: Albuquerque 63 fair; Anchorage 49 showery; Boise 52
partly cloudy; Casper 46 cloudy; Fairbanks 49 cloudy; Great Falls
34 snow; Honolulu 81 partly cloudy; Las Vegas 77 fair; Los Angeles
65 fair; Medford 58 cloudy; Pendleton 56 cloudy; Phoenix 88 fair;
Portland, Ore., 53 partly cloudy; Reno 58 fair; Salt Lake City 52
fair; San Diego 66 fair; San Francisco 57 fair; Seattle 56 fair;
