went, the rotund comedian says it was ``the hardest year I ever
lived through.''
   ``I lost my marriage, my children got very messed up. Then in a
three-month period I ended up with a new man, a new daughter, a new
house,'' the star of ``Roseanne'' said in this week's People
magazine.
   The new man is longtime friend Tom Arnold. The new daughter is
Brandi Brown, now 17, who Barr gave up for adoption as an infant.
