married. He's trying to lose 20,'' she said.
   ABC's Roseanne led the A.C. Nielsen Co. ratings in its season
premiere last month. Barr plays a blue-collar mom who _ until she
quit in the season finale last spring _ worked in a plastics
factory. She has three rambunctious kids and a husband who's
usually out of work.
