<HEAD>Power Failure Hits Manila, Second in Less Than a Week</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MANILA, Philippines (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The Phid no employees are expected to be laid off.
   The Times, established in 1865, has a circulation of just under
25,000, according to the 1989 Editor &amp; Publisher yearbook. The News
and Observer has a circulation of about 140,000 daily, 185,000
Sundays.
   Daniels said he made the decision to close the Times after
