Miller, 19, of Champion when it spun out of control on a rain-slick
highway. State police said the car crossed the center line and
collided with the truck. Miller also was killed.
   Neither Miller nor Pirl was wearing a seat belt, said Trooper
Stanley Foss.
   The truck driver was not injured.
